3chess changelog
Maciej Sobolewski


Version 0.2.3
Date: 31.03.2015
- Added interface classes.
- Undo button functionality implemented.

Version 0.2.2
Date: 24.03.2015
- Undo function implemented.

Version 0.2.1
Date: 24.03.2015
- First lines of undo function.
- Minor bugfixes.

Version 0.2
Date: 15.03.2015
- Stable enough to call it an alpha version.
- Minor bugfixes.
- Output modifications.
- Chosen one "animation".

Version 0.1.6
Date: 14.03.2015
- Turns recognition implemented.
- Ally/enemy recognition implemented.

Version 0.1.5
Date: 13.03.2015
- Moving and killing is now fully functional.
- Moves printing.
- Complete chessmen graphics implemented.
- Minor bugs fixing.

Version 0.1.4
Date: 11.03.2015
- First chessmen graphics added.
- Added functions for moving chessmen at mouse click.
- Modifications in chessmen class.
- Added basic language dictionary.

Version 0.1.3
Date: 02.03.2015
- Completly new square finding algorithm.

Version 0.1.2
Date: 15.02.2015
- Modified Chessman.move() function to work properly.
- Bad squares in alhorithm noticed and being hunted for.
- Repaired A4 bad square.

Version 0.1.1
Date: 01.10.2014 to 14.02.2015
- Main program.
- Board image.
- Resolution and squares algorithm.
- Basic classes and functions.



